Sokoto state Commissioner of Information, Barrister Bello Goronyo, has defected to the All Progressives Congress (APC). He announced his defection at the APC Governorship rally in Wamakko local government area same time when the ruling Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) was holding a mega rally at the hometown of Governor Aminu Waziri Tambuwal on Tuesday. Goronyo said he rejoined his former party because it has all it takes to move the state forward. Daily Trust learnt that the Commissioner was having a sour relationship with some leaders of PDP in the state. Tambuwalâ€™s biggest political gamble Nasarawa dep governor defects from APC to PDP Sokoto in 2018